<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Landing Page</title>
  
  <!-- Font Awesome CDN -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-KfkfwYDsLkIlwQp6LFnl8zNdLGxu9YAA1QvwINks4PhcElQSvqcyVLLD9aMhXd13uQjoXtEKNosOWaZqXgel0g==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* Full-screen background image from Pexels */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55)),
        url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/35546030/pexels-photo-35546030/free-photo-of-sunset-over-scenic-mountain-lake-landscape.jpeg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    
    .content {
      max-width: 800px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 3.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    
    p {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0066ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.35);
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #0055dd;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.5);
    }
    
    .icons {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
    }
    
    .icons a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 18px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .icons a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.25);
      color: #00d4ff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Amazing Product</h1>
      <p>Discover a new way to experience beauty, simplicity, and power. Start your journey today with tools designed for the modern world.</p>
      
      <a href="#get-started" class="btn">Get Started <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      
      <div class="icons">
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>